		(uuid "b75828a1-5e2a-4812-b288-f6e1de4da94a")
	)
	(text "N-channel MOSFET battery switch from BMU v2 BMU_switch_mosfet.kicad_sch.\nGate driver resistor: 10k (limits inrush to gate capacitance).\nGate pull-down: 100k (ensures OFF when control floating).\nFlyback/body diode: Schottky across drain-source for inductive loads.\nMOSFET: IRLZ44N or equivalent (Vds>=60V, Rds_on<25mOhm, logic-level gate).\nGATE_CTRL: 3.3V logic compatible (logic-level MOSFET) or use gate driver IC.\nMax continuous current depends on MOSFET selection and heatsinking.\nFrom KXKM Batterie Parallelator: 16-channel battery management (4x TCA9535 GPIO expanders)."
		(at 76.2 38.1 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.524 1.524)
			)
		)
